'''Jefferson Davis''' (Christian County, ([[Kentucky]]), [[3 di yüni]] [[1808]] - [[New Orleans]], [[6 di desember]] [[1889]]), tabata u   [[politiko]] i militar [[Estadonan Uni di Merka|merikano]]. Durante [[Guera Sivil Merikano]] e tabata e prome i uniko presidente di e [[Estadonan Konfederá di Merka]] di [[1861]] te [[1865]].

Jefferson tabata e yu mas yong dje famia Davis ku a emigrá for di [[Wales]]. E famia Davis a biba na [[Louisiana]] i [[Mississippi (estado)|Mississippi]]. Jefferson ku su ruman muhé Mary a bai Wilkinson Academy. Jefferson a sigui despues skol katoliko na Saint Rose Priory i na aña 1818 ela bai College na Washington djeí ela bai United States Military Academy (West Point). Jefferson a kasa 17 juni 1835 ku Sarah Knox Taylor ku a fayesé 3 luna despues 15 di september 1835.

